  <summary date="2015-06-15T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">21st Century STEM for Girls and Underrepresented Minorities Act

This bill amends the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 to authorize the Department of Education (ED) to provide grants to local educational agencies &#160;to encourage the ongoing development of programs and curricula for girls and underrepresented minorities in science, technology, engineering, and mathematics (STEM) and prepare those students&#160;to pursue undergraduate and graduate degrees and careers in such fields.</summary>
